summary:
I thought I could share some pictures from my Harry Potter birthday party last weekend with you Potterheads out there. ⚡
 I...
caption:
I thought I could share some pictures from my Harry Potter birthday party last weekend with you Potterheads out there. ⚡
I invited everyone a while back by sending them their Hogwarts acceptance letters.
When everyone arrived I had decorated the room with flying candles, black and golden colours for the great hall feelings and a pink Honeydukes sweet shop 😉
People’s houses were determined with little cookies that I filled with colour and everyone got a button of their house. And the best house (Slytherin 🐍🐍🐍) won the house cup in the end for some little games (like guessing how many golden chocolate snitches I had hidden in the room).
I had also created a potions booth with a hand-written potions book 😊
And my sister made me a cake like the one Hagrid brought Harry. 🎂
All in all, I thought this was really fun and great and that’s why I wanted to share it with you. 😁

the electronics of your heart…

The year is 2027. Nearly three decades have passed since the battle at Hogwarts and the wizarding world continues its uphill climb towards a slow, tumultuous recovery. Danger lurks around every corner as the possibility of a wizarding epidemic sends the wizarding community into a frenzy that brings a new evil to power.

see how fast they fall apart…

Will you fight for what you believe, or take the path of least resistance? Whether you flee or bite down and take the heat, the next great war is coming and the outcome is up to you. Welcome to Biting Down.
